title: GoPro: Hero Session (Our Most Durable Camera Yet)
description:
Small and light, with easy one-button control and rugged, waterproof design. HERO Session is perfect as a second GoPro camera, or for the first-time GoPro user who wants the simplest, grab- and-go capture experience.

Music
Jane's Addiction "Stop"
